    <div  style="border:1px solid #cecece;width:50%;text-align: center;">
        If you have any questions, please call us at (888) 681-8320 or (909)629-0869
        <br><br>
        Our office is located: <br>
        12330 Colony Ave. <br>
        Chino, CA 91710 <br>
        Hours: M-F from 0830 to 1700 PST
    </div>
</footer>
</html>